prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a young Asian couple, transformed into humorous cartoon characters, standing side-by-side and comically struggling to lift a giant, steaming, oversized bowl of dumplings that is almost as big as them. The man, on the right, has short, dark, textured hair and is wearing a tan hoodie and dark reddish-maroon pants; he's straining with a funny, exaggerated expression of effort. The woman, on the left, has long, straight, dark hair, is wearing gold-rimmed glasses, a light blue sweatshirt (with no text), and black pants; she's also showing a funny, strained look as she helps lift the heavy bowl. The scene is set against a simple, light-colored background with soft watercolor bleeds to keep the focus on the characters. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable, dark-colored handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Thanks for always feeding us, Lao Lao!". The overall style is lighthearted, with soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, and a visible paper texture.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
